casebody.data:
Justin Tait MITTON
v.
Candice H MITTON CV-17-0158-PR Supreme Court of Arizona. September 12, 2017 MINUTES ORDERED: Petition for Review = DENIED. FURTHER ORDERED: The Court of Appeals' Opinion shall not be published, pursuant to Rule 111(g), Arizona Rules of the Supreme Court. FURTHER ORDERED: Request for Costs (Appellee C. Mitton) = GRANTED.

Justice Gould voted to grant review.
